{
  "stem": "5516.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't fight 2 million against 45 million.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the war started, Hitler with Stalin made the agreement they will split Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Russia took off a big part of Poland-- Ukraine, they call this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took over Vilna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they took over Vilna, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they called up the Lithuanian government.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say, you didn't have Vilna never.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got now Vilna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We like to give you a present-- Vilna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you can come in and take over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll give you over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Lithuania mobilized all the recruits and the ex-soldiers, you know, just to take it over without war, the, the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was five miles from, from, from the border where they are now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They come over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russian hold them for three months near the border, and they didn't let them in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their excuse is they didn't say nobody because they cleaned out the city Vilna.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took out, out even the knobs from the doors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the city was cleared, then they let in the-- [LAUGHS] --the army, the Lithuanian army to take it over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they took it over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but after they took it over, they made bases there--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--see?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made bases.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lithuania couldn't refuse nothing because you cannot fight Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Russia is 350 million people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Russians made bases there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the Russians made bases, and they was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had-- in Panevezys, we had a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, but this rabbi was a elected member of the Lithuanian parliament even, see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he wasn't too much in the city Panevezys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was most in Africa or in the United State.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he used to go between the Jewish population and collect money.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
